<emphasis box="[486,598,1059,1084]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="117">nebulosus</emphasis>
” (foggy, cloudy) due the grayish pubescence of this species.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="10.[151,1437,151,1228]" box="[199,501,1095,1120]" pageId="10" pageNumber="117">
